Notice for Midterm Examinations of Spring Semester’20(For the Students of BUBT)
This is for information of all the registered students in different programs both Day and Evening shifts of BUBT that the Midterm Examinations of Spring Semester’2020 will be held from June 6, 2020 to June 13, 2020 through online (Google Classroom).

The detailed schedule of the examinations will be published by May 28, 2020;
Students are strictly advised to take preparation for the examinations;
Students are instructed to pay their outstanding dues before the examination;
It is to be noted that students who will pay their outstanding dues before the examinations can avail the 25% special tuition fee waiver for the Spring Semester’2020.

(Dr. Harun-or-Rashid)RegistrarBUBT

Applications in prescribed form are invited from the BUBT students of undergraduate programs for Scholarship/Stipend/Fee Waiver:

Students who are currently enjoying waiver in the categories of Freedom Fighter, Sibling, Spouse, and as students of Dhaka Commerce College are not required to apply;
Students who are enjoying wavier for results of the SSC and the HSC Examinations are not required to apply;
Newly admitted students having total CGPA/GPA of at least 7.00 in the SSC and the HSC are eligible to apply;
Current Students of BUBT who have obtained CGPA 3.00 and above are eligible to apply;
Application Forms are available at the Reception Desks free of cost. It can also be downloaded from the BUBT Website (www.bubt.edu.bd);
Completed Application Forms to be submitted to Room No. 211 of Building No -1 by February 27, 2020;
Incomplete Applications will not be considered.

 
(Dr. Md. Harun-or-Rashid)Registrar

All the departmental Chairmen of BUBT are requested to submit their departmental class routines in the following manner as early as possible to the undersigned.

Intake wise;
Intake teacher wise;
Room wise;
